1000 REM "Based on Host or remote call other programs
1010 IF W9$(7,1)="R" THEN GOSUB DO_REMOTE ELSE GOSUB DO_HOST
1095 GOTO 9900
2000 DO_REMOTE:REM "Process 3 process for the remote client
2010 MESS$="Preparing information to transfer to the host... "; GOSUB DO_MESSAGE; CALL "RT2PTA",X3$,X4$,"","*"
2020 REM TRANSFERRED TO RT2PTA: LET MESS$="Start Transfer process to host... "; GOSUB DO_MESSAGE; CALL "RT2TRN",X3$,X4$,"","*"
